OL,3,CDad of former Muckamore patient hopes
OL,4,Cinquiry changes safeguarding for good
OL,6,FThe inquiry was set up to find out the
OL,7,Fscale and extent of abuse at the
OL,8,Ffacility for adults with learning
OL,9,Fdisabilities run by Belfast Health and
OL,10,FSocial Care Trust, and the
OL,11,Fcircumstances that allowed it to
OL,12,Fhappen.
OL,14,FIt was examining the time period
OL,15,Fbetween 1999 and 2021.
OL,17,FThe hospital has also been at the
OL,18,Fcentre of the UK's largest ever police
OL,19,Finvestigation into the alleged abuse
OL,20,Fof vulnerable adults, and 15 people
OL,21,Fhave been charged to date.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
