OL,3,CDad of former Muckamore patient hopes
OL,4,Cinquiry changes safeguarding for good
OL,6,FGlynn Brown has been one of the core
OL,7,Fparticipants of the inquiry, and one
OL,8,Fof the voices shouting loudly for a
OL,9,Fprobe into Muckamore Abbey Hospital in
OL,10,Fthe first place.
OL,12,FIn 2017, he was shown CCTV footage as
OL,13,Fhe believed his son Aaron had been
OL,14,Fassaulted at the facility.
OL,16,FIt is understood that this footage set
OL,17,Fthe investigation in motion.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
