OL,3,CDad of former Muckamore patient hopes
OL,4,Cinquiry changes safeguarding for good
OL,6,FAaron, now 28, has a severe learning
OL,7,Fdifficulty, non-verbal hypertrophic
OL,8,Fcardiomyopathy, epilepsy and sensory
OL,9,Fissues.
OL,11,F"My motivation would be that once I'm
OL,12,Fdead, that I know the safeguarding
OL,13,Fprocesses and the regulatory bodies
OL,14,Fwill be in a much better place, and
OL,15,Fthat my son and others like him will
OL,16,Fbe safer where they are in their
OL,17,Fenvironment," said Mr Brown.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
