OL,3,CDad of former Muckamore patient hopes
OL,4,Cinquiry changes safeguarding for good
OL,6,FThe Senior Counsel to the Inquiry,
OL,7,FSean Doran KC, said the risk of
OL,8,Fprejudice will not inhibit the panel
OL,9,Ffrom making "the findings and
OL,10,Frecommendations that it regards as
OL,11,Fappropriate."
OL,13,F"The inquiry has operated and will
OL,14,Fcontinue to operate with sensitivity
OL,15,Fto the live nature of criminal
OL,16,Fproceedings that may conceivably
OL,17,Fextend for some time beyond the life
OL,18,Fof the inquiry," he said.
