OL,3,CDad of former Muckamore patient hopes
OL,4,Cinquiry changes safeguarding for good
OL,6,F"Throughout the duration of the
OL,7,Fhearings, the Inquiry team has liaised
OL,8,Fregularly with PSNI and Public
OL,9,FProsecution Service and has sought to
OL,10,Fensure ... that the procedure and
OL,11,Fconduct of the Inquiry has respected
OL,12,Fthe integrity of the investigation and
OL,13,Fprosecutions, while continuing to
OL,14,Faddress the Terms of Reference. "
OL,16,FThe Terms of Reference are the
OL,17,Fobjectives the inquiry was tasked with
OL,18,Fachieving when it was established.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
