OL,3,CDad of former Muckamore patient hopes
OL,4,Cinquiry changes safeguarding for good
OL,6,F"While appropriate measures have been
OL,7,Ftaken to protect against the risk of
OL,8,Fprejudice to the criminal proceedings,
OL,9,Fthose measures have involved the least
OL,10,Fpossible restriction on public access
OL,11,Fto the proceedings," he said.
OL,13,FMr Doran acknowledged that families
OL,14,Fsuffered pain "beyond our
OL,15,Fcomprehension" while learning about
OL,16,F"what endured in the hospital."
OL,18,FHe also paid tribute to two
OL,19,Fparticipants who have passed away
OL,20,Fwithout learning the outcomes of the
OL,21,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
