OL,6,FSocial worker Geraldine O'Hagan gave
OL,7,Fevidence in her dying days.
OL,9,F"She provided unwavering support to
OL,10,Fthose families prior to and in the
OL,11,Fcourse of the Inquiry," he said.
OL,13,F"She attended the Inquiry on 15 May
OL,14,F2024 and gave her evidence with the
OL,15,Fsupport of her son Josh.
OL,17,F"Geraldine passed away on 10 June 2024.
