OL,3,CDad of former Muckamore patient hopes
OL,4,Cinquiry changes safeguarding for good
OL,6,F"The fortitude that Geraldine
OL,7,Fdisplayed in assisting the Panel in
OL,8,Fthe face of serious illness will
OL,9,Fsurely live long in the memory of all
OL,10,Fof us involved in this Inquiry."
OL,12,FMr Doran said that nurse Eileen
OL,13,FMcLarnon worked at the hospital from
OL,14,F1972 until her retirement in 2016.
OL,16,F"She provided the Inquiry with a
OL,17,Fdetailed statement which was read to
OL,18,Fthe Panel on Tuesday 06 February
OL,19,F2024... Eileen passed away on 12 April
OL,20,F2024."
