OL,3,CDad of former Muckamore patient hopes
OL,4,Cinquiry changes safeguarding for good
OL,6,FThere has been a series of apologies
OL,7,Fmade to the families and victims over
OL,8,Fthe course of the 120 sitting days of
OL,9,Fthe inquiry.
OL,11,FThe Belfast Trust's lawyer told the
OL,12,Finquiry the Trust reiterates its
OL,13,Fapology to patients and families.
OL,15,FJoseph Aiken KC said: "I recognise on
OL,16,Fbehalf of the Belfast Trust that... it
OL,17,Fwas said that saying sorry was not
OL,18,Fsufficient.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
